    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Laguna Seca Blue. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. Shifting is handled by a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically impeccable, the rod bearings and Vanos system have been proactively serviced to ensure longevity. The chassis remains structurally flawless with a reinforced subframe and original bushings. Riding on forged Style 67 wheels with fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, this M3 offers unparalleled analog feedback and razor-sharp turn-in. A true turn-key icon for the discerning purist.",
